 situation when a mistake is uncovered? Will you be able to redo the strict minimum data handling?","uuid":"c076b732-5c75-475d-8ff2-77455d999c24","entityUuid":"02b3fed1-0b50-4a80-b8b6-a225a1107022","questionType":"OptionsQuestion","parentUuid":"6d18bfff-0f53-469b-934e-9806dda9d4fb","eventType":"AddQuestionEvent","title":"Did you consider how to monitor data integrity?","requiredPhaseUuid":"1796fa3c-9f53-475f-89ff-c66a0453c42e"},{"annotations":[],"createdAt":"2018-10-01T00:00:00Z","uuid":"d6b3bb42-984c-438d-bf74-087092c48e36","entityUuid":"fc0d8147-e363-44c1-ae7d-204da22f2675","parentUuid":"02b3fed1-0b50-4a80-b8b6-a225a1107022","eventType":"AddReferenceEvent","shortUuid":"spg","referenceType":"ResourcePageReference"},{"annotations":[],"advice":null,"createdAt":"2018-10-01T00:00:00Z","uuid":"1c1225ea-decf-4d26-a439-ad96ee3c45d2","entityUuid":"8608d3df-7d7f-4893-8f80-e5297167b213","parentUuid":"02b3fed1-0b50-4a80-b8b6-a225a1107022","eventType":"AddAnswerEvent","metricMeasures":[],"label":"Explore"},{"annotations":[],"tagUuids":[],"createdAt":"2018-10-01T00:00:00Z","text":"Data corruption or mistakes can happen with large amounts of files or large files. Keeping a master list with data checksums can be helpful to prevent expensive mistakes. It can also be helpful to keep the sample list under version control forcing that all changes are well documented.","uuid":"9819ac8e-b9fe-4c8c-a41c-13c26daec47c","entityUuid":"e0759fdc-7ce9-4020-816d-73119f634c7e","questionType":"OptionsQuestion","parentUuid":"8608d3df-7d7f-4893-8f80-e5297167b213","eventType":"AddQuestionEvent","title":"Will you be keeping a master list with checksums of certified/correct/canonical/verified data?","requiredPhaseUuid":"1796fa3c-9f53-475f-89ff-c66a0453c42e"},{"annotations":[],"advice":null,"createdAt":"2018-10-01T00:00:00Z","uuid":"1e3b4a72-c0a9-4027-8267-634d8efbc070","entityUuid":"637f4603-0a24-47d1-a2f7-96958b4841fd","parentUuid":"e0759fdc-7ce9-4020-816d-73119f634c7e","eventType":"AddAnswerEvent","m