ss the different compute infrastructures you are using?","requiredPhaseUuid":"1796fa3c-9f53-475f-89ff-c66a0453c42e"},{"annotations":[],"advice":null,"createdAt":"2018-10-01T00:00:00Z","uuid":"723dd950-20d4-4a80-9d05-2105b5239855","entityUuid":"8d038086-a207-46f4-9e7c-180780d9c3a6","parentUuid":"e8a08f27-9f82-4147-b446-822d34a5d468","eventType":"AddAnswerEvent","metricMeasures":[{"weight":1,"measure":0,"metricUuid":"0bafe0c2-a8f2-4c74-80c8-dbf3a5b8e9b7"}],"label":"No"},{"annotations":[],"advice":null,"createdAt":"2018-10-01T00:00:00Z","uuid":"5d7b19e9-32cc-4125-b7e9-0c0657b27c4b","entityUuid":"be0761b6-421a-4683-8ff9-de496868feea","parentUuid":"e8a08f27-9f82-4147-b446-822d34a5d468","eventType":"AddAnswerEvent","metricMeasures":[{"weight":1,"measure":1,"metricUuid":"0bafe0c2-a8f2-4c74-80c8-dbf3a5b8e9b7"}],"label":"Yes"},{"annotations":[],"tagUuids":[],"createdAt":"2018-10-01T00:00:00Z","text":"Surrounding all tools in your data processing and analysis workflows with the ''boilerplate'' code necessary on the computer system you are using is tedious and error prone. Especially if you are using the same tools in multiple different work flows and/or on multiple different computer architectures. Automated instrumentation, e.g. by using a workflow management system, can prevent many mistakes.","uuid":"ac4c8e66-a70b-4c63-bf2b-a3a259e501ca","entityUuid":"a3a4ce37-4ced-41df-8ec6-e42d87a6a3f1","questionType":"OptionsQuestion","parentUuid":"30d1e85c-0e3e-482f-97f9-22a7658b329e","eventType":"AddQuestionEvent","title":"Will you be instrumenting the tools into pipelines and workflows using automated tools?","requiredPhaseUuid":"1796fa3c-9f53-475f-89ff-c66a0453c42e"},{"annotations":[],"advice":null,"createdAt":"2018-10-01T00:00:00Z","uuid":"24d697e9-b03b-4db5-8e2c-caacc1ce04ae","entityUuid":"9ffbb7f2-5eb8-455a-bd98-6547887e0eb6","parentUuid":"a3a4ce37-4ced-41df-8ec6-e42d87a6a3f1","eventType":"AddAnswerEvent","metricMeasures":[{"weight":1,"measure":0,"metricUuid":"0bafe0c2-a8f2-4c74-